channel.title: Upload the cache to another host please!
channel.description:
hello Everytime I try to download the cache (from netfirms) it stops at 1.82mb (This is not from my connection, I just downloaded a 60mb file) can you post mirrors (other than rapidshare) here for it please, it could help other people :D
I am talking about this cache: [b]http://www.moparisthebest.com/cache/cache.zip[/b]
BTW: Im sure that this is happening with this dude also: http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,18014.0.html[br][size=1]Posted at: September 02, 2006, 06:36:47 AM[/size][hr]I just want to someone to upload the cache to another host please !!! I searched this forum maybe I could find something and it turns out that this is happening with Lots and lots of people !!
